## Dataset
Added papers, now 99 total (85 train / 14 test)
Added tokens check, only one example slightly goes over the 2048 limit
Empty-ratio set to 100000, keep all negative chunks
Train/test split info is now saved

## Train
Quantization
- Before: 4-bit NF4 (QLoRA) always
- Now: bf16 by default; --load_in_4bit flag for low-VRAM
LoRA rank
- Before: r=16, alpha=32
- Now: r=32 (configurable via --lora_r), alpha=64
LoRA modules
- Before: q, k, v, o only
- Now: + gate, up, down (MLP projections)
Gradient checkpointing
- Before: always enabled
- Now: removed
Batch size
- Before: 1
- Now: 1
Grad accumulation
- Before: 8
- Now: 8
Effective batch
- Before: 8
- Now: 8
max_length
- Before: 3072
- Now: 2048
eval_steps
- Before: 200
- Now: 50
save_steps
- Before: 200
- Now: 50
New arg
- Before: —
- Now: --lora_r 32

